Downlaod and analyze the UCCCC new student pickup data

1.Student gender: clearly, we picked up many more female students than male students.

2.University: most of the students we picked up are UPenn students.

3.Degree: most of the students we master students. We picked up more visiting scholar than PhD students.

4.University and gender: again, most of the students we picked up are UPenn students and most of them are female students.

5.University and degree: most of the students are master students. No bachelor degree student from UPenn, all bachelor degree students are from Drexel.

6.Degree and gender: again, most of the students we picked up are UPenn students and most of them are female students.

7. Major: enginerring, education and design are the top 3 majors for students we picked upt.

8. Major ans gender: interestingly, most majors have more female students than male students, except enginerring and communication.
